<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="confident-adj">confident <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɒnfɪdənt/    美 /'kɒnfədənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>有信心的；自信的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a conﬁdent smile</strong>
自信的微笑</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>确信的；有把握的：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>(be) conﬁdent about sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I feel conﬁdent about the interview.
我对面试很有把握。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should not mind what others say so long as we are confident about what we have done.
只要我们对自己所做的事有信心，就不该在意别人说什么。</p><footer>2012 北京书面表达</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) conﬁdent of (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are confident of our success.
我们对成功坚信不疑。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) conﬁdent + that 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are confident that the environment will be improved by our further efforts.
我们相信，通过我们进一步的努力环境将会得到改善。</p><footer>2013 辽宁改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>confidently /'kɒnfədəntlɪ/ adv   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The little girl walked <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (自信地) onto the stage, ready for her first speech.  （2012 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. confidently  </p></div>